<div class="status-header">
    <div class="tag" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #166534;">MATERIAL READY</div>
    <h1>Ready for Dispatch</h1>
    <p>Good news! Material for Order #{{orderId}} is ready at the seller's yard.</p>
</div>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Order Number</div>
        <div class="info-value">#{{orderId}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Seller Location</div>
        <div class="info-value">{{pickupCity}}</div>
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Logistics Details</h3>
<p>
    <strong>Mode:</strong> {{logisticsPreference}}<br>
    <strong>Next Action:</strong> 
    {{#if is3PL}}
        Platform Admin will now award the 3PL bid to a carrier.
    {{else}}
        Please arrange for your vehicle pickup as per the agreed incoterms.
    {{/if}}
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    <a href="{{ctaUrl}}" class="btn">Track Order Execution</a>
</div>
